&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;For those who continue to so &lt;strong&gt;fondly&lt;/strong&gt; refer to me as a half-baked chef, you have forced my hand. I&#039;ve said it before and I&#039;ll echo it ten thousand times more. Art belongs on the wall, not on a plate.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
